Alternatively, appointments at  <span class="termsBold"> Spire Harpenden </span>( 0800 585 112 ), <span class="termsBold"> Clementine Churchill </span>( 0808 101 0337 ),<span class="termsBold"> Priory Wellbeing Fenchurch St </span>(0207 398 0008 ) and <span class="termsBold"> The Holly Private Hospital </span>( 0208 936 1201 ) can be made directly.<br/><br/>
